{"tid":1810550,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"牛奶公司持美心一半股權，佢唔同美心集團割席，我地割","createTime":"2020-01-04T03:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T03:50:27.000Z","uid":273188,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82ef53b448120286a919f7470902e1ec9eac5936","tid":1810550,"uid":273188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:37:52.000Z","msg":"美心已經係全民共識，<br />\n要建立黃色經濟圈，首要建立戰積，一定要令佢倒閉。唔幫襯佢，令佢無生意，最後倒閉。<br />\n牛奶公司持美心一半股權，佢在美心公司有極大的影響，但仍然唔行駛影響力，繼續支持藍絲。<br />\n所以我地支持政府的宣傳口號，要與藍絲的暴力割席，都要同牛奶公司割席。<br />\n<br />\n總結罷買日活動經驗，我們可以嘗試擴大戰線，但要運動有效，一定要集中戰火。<br />\n所以，要集中對付美心，我地要發掘和美心有關的企業都要受到罷買的懲罰。"},{"pid":"47b1a8f97ed47add573960ae82592431864440f5","tid":1810550,"uid":71218,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"牛奶工司一早出賣手足,71提供閉路錄音比黑驚,一早要罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d32b7f93301ec164bc24dc94995defb6c579888","tid":1810550,"uid":189138,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:43:10.000Z","msg":"先紅"},{"pid":"482466a5119f8bc87b4957583f91e14edcfabb72","tid":1810550,"uid":273188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47b1a8f97ed47add573960ae82592431864440f5","tid":1810550,"uid":71218,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:42:30.000Z","msg":"牛奶工司一早出賣手足,71提供閉路錄音比黑驚,一早要罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔明白，高登個個哈佛畢業，無可能唔明咩係持股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解罷買美心，但唔罷買持股美心成50%的牛奶公司。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c383f8530ada4c133991d753c426b83954844810","tid":1810550,"u